text: Funky Divas is a new jack swing-R&B; studio album from 1992 by American group En Vogue. The album had the songs "Free Your Mind", "My Lovin' (You're Never Gonna Get It)" and "Giving Him Something He Can Feel". It sold five million records worldwide. This album was released on March 24, 1992. Category:1992 albums Category:R&B; albums Category:En Vogue albums
title: Funky Divas
